{"tid":1954637,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愛斯賓奴好消息！武磊等6名確診者已康復","createTime":"2020-04-02T03:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T03:54:23.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8d9d39e86ab20a7cc686d9ef782250646ae925","tid":1954637,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"西班牙媒體《每日體育報》報導稱，愛斯賓奴感染新冠病毒的6人已經全部康復。<br />\n<br />\n  該報從愛斯賓奴球會方面證實，愛斯賓奴感染新冠病毒的6人已經全部康復，目前他們正在隔離之中。這6人中，包括5名球員和1名教練組成員，後者也是最後一位康復的感染者。<br />\n<br />\n西媒稱武磊等人已經康復<br />\n<br />\n  愛斯賓奴並未公佈6名感染者的姓名，不過中國球員武磊（Wu Lei）等人已經通過其他渠道確認自己感染。<br />\n<br />\n  現在6人均在家休息，嚴格遵守15天的隔離期。昨天剛剛康復的教練員也將居家隔離15天，這也是世界衛生組織所要求的：「康復患者要在家中隔離，以便阻絕病毒的傳播。」"},{"pid":"d6082b1244e7579669757a92fcfa9fe8d03c223c","tid":1954637,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bb4f55da8457448d7501efc2293296c914ffed","tid":1954637,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqFFXhu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqFFXhu.png&h=f796087d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"718b9a057fcd021dd4d429c009f549fd57c7699e","tid":1954637,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"武磊肺已花，躝返支國等死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}